# Synaps default config — baked into synaps-burnout at /root/.synaps-cli/config
#
# `identity` is REQUIRED for OAuth / broker-vended Anthropic credentials:
# Anthropic only accepts Claude Pro/Max OAuth tokens from the Claude Code client
# identity, so the first system block must declare it. Without this, broker mode
# (SYNAPS_AUTH_ENDPOINT) and mounted-OAuth calls are rejected/hang.
# Not needed for a raw ANTHROPIC_API_KEY — but harmless there.
identity = You are Claude Code, Anthropic's official CLI for Claude.
